\begin_inset Formula $\theta$
\end_inset

 的正实数 
\begin_inset Formula $\delta$
\end_inset

，使得在 
\begin_inset Formula $\forall\rho\in(0,\delta)$
\end_inset

 的圆弧 
\begin_inset Formula $C_{a,\rho}$
\end_inset

 上都有
\begin_inset Formula 
\[
