，代入导数定义即得
\begin_inset Formula 
\[
F'(z)=\lim_{h\to0}\frac{F(z+h)-F(z)}{h}=\lim_{h\to0}\left(\int_{a}^{z+h}-\int_{a}^{z}\right)\frac{f(\zeta)}{h}\dd{\zeta}=\lim_{h\to0}\int_{z}^{z+h}\frac{f(z)+\varepsilon(\zeta)}{h}\dd{\zeta}
\]

\end_inset

在由 
\begin_inset Formula $z$
\end_inset

